{"tid":13950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做左三年戲院 你問我答","createTime":"2016-11-30T09:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T12:56:13.000Z","uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"50fa995fdd2ad7e7d756fbd612146cef9f6371fd","tid":13950,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"返工地點唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c945eecf2de21f828aa9976b2f17eb213ad81359","tid":13950,"uid":43072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:52:38.000Z","msg":"到底拎住個M記入去食係咪唔會比職員話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a3099143db5eec1f7c403c3db8ce9dd7bdda5c","tid":13950,"uid":41613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:55:31.000Z","msg":"啲櫈有無愛滋針？"},{"pid":"f42bf37a2add2cc56139daf93d4a2e8198db9f6e","tid":13950,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底拎住個M記入去食係咪唔會比職員話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你收埋係書包或者同熟客<br />\n都當睇唔到<br />\n但好多on9仔又要明目張膽咁拎住入去<br />\n捉到又黑面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外，食外帶食物好心有手尾自己執埋啦"},{"pid":"86215a8b8ab3917b4551c0ea395a80281cbddf42","tid":13950,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"有無得免費睇戲？"},{"pid":"c0ced3797bf332cf86bf4a08947d477452f147d2","tid":13950,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲櫈有無愛滋針？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實長期都唔會清潔<br />\n有次有個bb賴屎係張櫈到<br />\n我地拎紙同水，清下佢<br />\n噴兩野空氣清新劑<br />\n又再開返間院<br />\n已經冇講到平時啲爆谷碎同汽水漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0faca5837f4a293efa03654235fabeedfc8fc582","tid":13950,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無得免費睇戲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經理或會報串既同事都唔係到<br />\n其實可以放人 入去坐冇人買飛既空位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d9eab407e8998b3b9b29f95b047c9cb16de43f","tid":13950,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"有冇鬼故?"},{"pid":"43224b731435ca849aa4a4d11e296dc45473a86c","tid":13950,"uid":42164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲櫈有無愛滋針？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實長期都唔會清潔<br />\n有次有個bb賴屎係張櫈到<br />\n我地拎紙同水，清下佢<br />\n噴兩野空氣清新劑<br />\n又再開返間院<br />\n已經冇講到平時啲爆谷碎同汽水漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"b0f44a8523397795059901e3e1d588237c504d8f","tid":13950,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"最近呢個令月有冇換過制服"},{"pid":"1daabbfecbd8ef5e289341620b7743a963a019f7","tid":13950,"uid":45276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"mk百記做過3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743ff47b5fef3dd4f380e7b407c4dacf630af378","tid":13950,"uid":10051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"有冇鬼故講嚟聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1c14d1ac3b4febb03a2bbb61a58ab3e36abc22","tid":13950,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:31:13.000Z","msg":"多唔多人睇戲時扑嘢"},{"pid":"3e9d755c92af03adfea6605cffb011d45fe7bf36","tid":13950,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近呢個令月有冇換過制服</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇喎，天氣凍著左長就"},{"pid":"672317ef0717636284fbdeab5227fa2e9b1b4a40","tid":13950,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇鬼故講嚟聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話說我果間戲院有個傳說<br />\n收尾果場唔好嘗試數院內既客人人頭<br />\n因為會數多或數少人數<br />\n咁有一次有個同事就唔信邪<br />\n真係走去數<br />\n當散完場出返黎個同事塊面都青曬<br />\n問佢做咩事，但佢死都唔講<br />\n之後仲辭埋職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s.呢件事係我聽返黎"},{"pid":"daeb3e66980e99d7b180210dcab2b3edaeca55e8","tid":13950,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:01:47.000Z","msg":"邊間<br />\n人工幾多<br />\n同事之間關係點<br />\n有冇見過情侶摷<br />\n見過最過份嘅客係點？"},{"pid":"2e5599bf417dadcb2ca75fd68c5619d925571589","tid":13950,"uid":12712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">邊間</span><br />\n人工幾多<br />\n同事之間關係點<br />\n有冇見過情侶摷<br />\n見過最過份嘅客係點？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48125e1800ccac24a09986383cfb72ce96aabe9b","tid":13950,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">邊間</span><br />\n人工幾多<br />\n同事之間關係點<br />\n有冇見過情侶摷<br />\n見過最過份嘅客係點？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思係百老匯定ua定抑或其他細戲院 唔係喺邊到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9ce4dfd5bdd945e74cb4f91c9c371cc578ebd6","tid":13950,"uid":8703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">邊間</span><br />\n人工幾多<br />\n同事之間關係點<br />\n有冇見過情侶摷<br />\n見過最過份嘅客係點？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑死"},{"pid":"efac900a37d783c894844e67136187a8201d20e1","tid":13950,"uid":844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">邊間</span><br />\n人工幾多<br />\n同事之間關係點<br />\n有冇見過情侶摷<br />\n見過最過份嘅客係點？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cb3f3349b715d8d9074ad478552af32c7d3a35","tid":13950,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多唔多人睇戲時扑嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔多，但執過安全套同kt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扑野就未見過<br />\n條女嗚低身幫條仔含撚就見過"},{"pid":"c2c0e830ff9a2820fdbd64d776ee85f60c9d2b3a","tid":13950,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲櫈有無愛滋針？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實長期都唔會清潔<br />\n有次有個bb賴屎係張櫈到<br />\n我地拎紙同水，清下佢<br />\n噴兩野空氣清新劑<br />\n又再開返間院<br />\n已經冇講到平時啲爆谷碎同汽水漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屌你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8779faf119ac9a2d98805ea0f107a9a234339d","tid":13950,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇鬼故講嚟聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話說我果間戲院有個傳說<br />\n收尾果場唔好嘗試數院內既客人人頭<br />\n因為會數多或數少人數<br />\n咁有一次有個同事就唔信邪<br />\n真係走去數<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當散完場出返黎個同事塊面都青曬<br />\n問佢做咩事，但佢死都唔講<br />\n之後仲辭埋職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s.呢件事係我聽返黎</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好流喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4681ed07c386d7aae8388335bb0dbc2caa1e65f6","tid":13950,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲櫈有無愛滋針？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實長期都唔會清潔<br />\n有次有個bb賴屎係張櫈到<br />\n我地拎紙同水，清下佢<br />\n噴兩野空氣清新劑<br />\n又再開返間院<br />\n已經冇講到平時啲爆谷碎同汽水漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屌你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bc8b88328ccaafa7ebed493ceac69260e188c2","tid":13950,"uid":44313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"好好奇想知你係邊間院線"}]}